title: Rustic Wooden Picture Frame by Heritage Home Decor - 8x10
description: The Rustic Wooden Picture Frame by Heritage Home Decor adds a touch of rustic charm to your home. Crafted from reclaimed wood, this 8x10 picture frame has a unique and authentic look. Showcase your favorite photographs and create a cozy, inviting atmosphere with this beautifully crafted frame.
